# Dropdown

Dropdown menu component for displaying contextual options and actions.

## Components

- **Dropdown** - `resources/views/components/ui/dropdown.blade.php`
- **Dropdown Item** - `resources/views/components/ui/dropdown/item.blade.php`
- **Dropdown Divider** - `resources/views/components/ui/dropdown/divider.blade.php`

## Features

- Left/Right alignment
- Customizable width
- Icon support for menu items
- Divider lines between items
- Link and button modes
- Danger variant for destructive actions
- Livewire support
- Dark mode compatible

## Usage

### Basic Dropdown

```blade
<x-ui.dropdown align="right" width="56">
    <x-slot:trigger>
        <button>Options</button>
    </x-slot:trigger>

    <x-ui.dropdown.item href="{{ route('profile') }}" wire:navigate>
        Profile
    </x-ui.dropdown.item>

    <x-ui.dropdown.divider />

    <x-ui.dropdown.item variant="danger" wire:click="logout">
        Logout
    </x-ui.dropdown.item>
</x-ui.dropdown>
```

